  "shortDescription": "Turn a few words into stunning AI character images in seconds.",
  "description": "Create AI characters from simple words.\nAI Image Character Generator Pro turns your imagination into unique character-based images in seconds. Just type a short description — a futuristic warrior, a mysterious girl, a fantasy hero, or any character in your mind — and let AI create the visual for you.\nNo design skills are needed. The app is built for writers, storytellers, game creators, artists, and content makers who want to quickly bring original characters to life.\nWith a simple interface and support for different visual styles, you can explore ideas, generate concepts, and turn a few words into inspiring images instantly.\nDescribe it. Generate it. Bring your character to life.\n",
